OL,3,CCompetitor dies in Jim Clark Rally
OL,5,FA competitor has died in a crash at
OL,6,Fthe Jim Clark Rally in the Borders.
OL,8,FCo-driver Dai Roberts was confirmed to
OL,9,Fhave died after the incident on the
OL,10,FEdrom Mains road near Duns shortly
OL,11,Fbefore 11am on Saturday 24th May.
OL,13,FDriver James Williams was taken by
OL,14,Fambulance to the Royal Infirmary of
OL,15,FEdinburgh with serious but not life
OL,16,Fthreatening injuries.
OL,18,FTributes to the Welshman, reportedly
OL,19,Ffrom Carmarthen, have been led by
OL,20,FJames Williams Rallying team.
