OL,5,FIts statement said: "It is with a
OL,6,Fheavy heart, we have to share this sad
OL,7,Fnews this afternoon.
OL,9,F"The motorsport community is deeply
OL,10,Fsaddened to learn of the passing of
OL,11,Four beloved Dai Roberts - who lost his
OL,12,Flife in an incident at the Jim Clark
OL,13,FRally on Saturday 24 May 2025."
OL,15,FIt added its "thoughts and prayers are
OL,16,Fwith the Roberts family at this
OL,17,Fdifficult time".
