OL,3,CCompetitor dies in Jim Clark Rally
OL,5,FThe sport's governing body, Motorsport
OL,6,FUK, has begun what it calls a "full
OL,7,Finvestigation" into the circumstances,
OL,8,Fworking with event organisers and the
OL,9,FJim Clark Memorial Motor Club.
OL,11,FIn a statement it said: "Motorsport UK
OL,12,Fsends its condolences to Dai's family
OL,13,Fand friends, the Jim Clark Rally, Jim
OL,14,FClark Memorial Motor Club and members
OL,15,Fof the motorsport community."
