OL,3,CCompetitor dies in Jim Clark Rally
OL,5,FFollowing the incident, the Jim Clark
OL,6,FMemorial Motor Club posted on X to say
OL,7,Fit had decided to cancel the remainder
OL,8,Fof the event as well as the Jim Clark
OL,9,FReivers Rally which was due to take
OL,10,Fplace on Sunday 25th May.
OL,12,FPolice Scotland confirmed that no one
OL,13,Felse was injured in the crash.
OL,15,FSuperintendent Vincent Fisher from
OL,16,FPolice Scotland said: "Our thoughts
OL,17,Fare with the family of the man who has
OL,18,Fdied and enquiries are ongoing to
OL,19,Festablish the full circumstances."
